headline: Prudential (PRU) Surpasses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Prudential (PRU) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +16.39% and +15.93%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: 1 S&P 500 Stock to Target This Week and 2 We Brush Off
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is often seen as a benchmark for strong businesses, but that doesn’t mean every stock is worth owning. Some companies face significant challenges, whether it’s stagnating growth, heavy debt, or disruptive new competitors.
